  凸体的Steiner对称化的两个定理
  Two Theorems of Steiner Symmetrization on Convex Bodies
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>孙</surname><given-names>丽英</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sub>1</sub></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff1"><label>1</label><addr-line>陕西师范大学，数学与信息科学学院，陕西 西安</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>1160097663@qq.com</email></corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>21</day><month>08</month><year>2017</year></pub-date><volume>07</volume><issue>05</issue><fpage>368</fpage><lpage>372</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014</copyright-year><license><license-p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY). http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>
 
 
   
   本文研究Steiner对称化在凸体上的充分条件。首先，我们根据Steiner对称化的性质，例如：保体积、保凸性、单调性、表面积减小等，构造一个凸体的变换 。其次，我们依据 满足的条件及Steiner对称化的概念，证明出 为凸体上的Steiner对称化，并且得到两个类似的推论。本文最后构造出了Steiner对称化的两个充分条件。 In this paper, we mainly study sufficient conditions for Steiner symmetrization on convex bodies. Firstly, according to the properties of Steiner symmetrization, such as volume-preserving, convexity-preserving, monotonicity, surface area reduction and so on, we constructed a transformation on convex bodies. Secondly, in accordance to Steiner symmetrization’s characterization and concept, we proved that is Steiner symmetrization and came up with two homologous corollaries. Finally, we obtained two sufficient conditions for Steiner symmetrization.
    
  
 
</p></abstract><kwd-group><kwd>凸体，Steiner对称化，Minkowski对称，超平面, Convex Body</kwd><kwd> Steiner Symmetrization</kwd><kwd> Minkowski Symmetrization</kwd><kwd> Hyperplane</kwd></kwd-group></article-meta></front><body><sec id="s1"><title>凸体的Steiner对称化的两个定理<sup> </sup></title><p>孙丽英</p><p>陕西师范大学，数学与信息科学学院，陕西 西安</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula64"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x6_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收稿日期：2017年8月1日；录用日期：2017年8月16日；发布日期：2017年8月21日</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula65"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x7_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s2"><title>摘 要</title><p>本文研究Steiner对称化在凸体上的充分条件。首先，我们根据Steiner对称化的性质，例如：保体积、保凸性、单调性、表面积减小等，构造一个凸体的变换<img src="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x8_hanspub.png" />。其次，我们依据<img src="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x9_hanspub.png" />满足的条件及Steiner对称化的概念，证明出<img src="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x10_hanspub.png" />为凸体上的Steiner对称化，并且得到两个类似的推论。本文最后构造出了Steiner对称化的两个充分条件。</p><p>关键词 :凸体，Steiner对称化，Minkowski对称，超平面</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula66"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x11_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>Copyright &#169; 2017 by author and Hans Publishers Inc.</p><p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY).</p><p>http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</p><p><img src="http://image.hanspub.org:8080\Html/htmlimages\1-2890033x\e70a10f1-7c93-45ea-9603-062237856e4b.png" /><img src="http://image.hanspub.org:8080\Html\htmlimages\1-2890033x\e898c85e-ffc4-45c9-b817-14224a4d6960.png" /></p></sec><sec id="s3"><title>1. 引言</title><p>1836年，Jakob Steiner介绍了凸体Steiner对称化的过程，并利用Steiner对称化尝试着证明了经典的等周不等式和经典的Brunn-Minkowski不等式，这在 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref1">1</xref>] 中第九章有详细证明过程。凸体在做Steiner对称化后，它还有些重要的性质，例如：体积不变、保凸性、单调性、直径不增等，这些性质在 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref2">2</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref3">3</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref4">4</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref5">5</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref6">6</xref>] 中可以查看，以及一般的紧集也可以做Steiner对称化，这可以在 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref7">7</xref>] 中查看。除了在几何方向有着重要作用外，Steiner对称化还在分析及PDE方向起着重要的作用。</p><p>我们要研究的问题是Steiner对称化的反问题，即构造一个在凸体上的变换<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x14_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，它在满足哪些条件的情况下，使之成为Steiner对称？事实上这个问题的答案是肯定的，我们得到了两个定理，在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x15_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足保体积、单调性等条件时，确定可以证明出其为Steiner对称化。在 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref8">8</xref>] 中讨论了Steiner对称，Minkowski对称，中心对称等，其中就研究了Steiner对称化的反问题，也得出了Steiner对称化的两个漂亮的定理。本文通过构造与其不同的条件，简洁地得出Steiner对称化反问题的两个定理。</p><p>上述出现的相关概念与记号，将在后文中做详细叙述。</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>2. 预备知识</title><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x16_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x17_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上全体凸体(紧凸集)构成的集合，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x18_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示单位球面，令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x19_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为欧几里德范数为1的向量，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x20_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x21_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是以<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x22_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为法向且过原点的超平面，这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x23_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x24_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中通常的内积。我们用<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x25_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x26_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于法向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x27_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的Steiner对称，以下是它的定义 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref5">5</xref>] ：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula67"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x28_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x31_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x32_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示线段<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x33_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的长度。</p><p>注意：由Steiner对称的定义可容易得出：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula68"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x34_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>且集合<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x36_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>对称。</p><p>下面我们列出一些Steiner对称的性质定理，这将会在后文证明中用到。</p><p>命题2.1 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref1">1</xref>] <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x37_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>命题2.2 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref1">1</xref>] <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x38_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x39_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示体积。</p><p>命题2.3 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref1">1</xref>] <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x40_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x41_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>命题2.4 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref1">1</xref>] 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x42_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>命题2.5 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref5">5</xref>] <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x44_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>命题2.6 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref9">9</xref>] <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的正交投影。</p><p>说明：这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>非必要条件，但在后文中只需要<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>即可，其他情况将不作讨论。</p><p>Minkowski对称有些好的性质，它与Steiner对称化有一些好的关系 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref5">5</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref10">10</xref>] 。</p><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于法向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的Minkowski对称为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x54_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，它的定义如下：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula69"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x55_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x56_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x58_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的反射，也就是作<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x60_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x61_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的对称变换。那么当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>对称时，有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，我们也很容易得到<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x65_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为一个线性算子，即：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula70"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x66_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>引理2.7 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21748-ref5">5</xref>] <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x67_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x68_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>证明设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x69_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x70_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x71_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的正交投影上的一个点，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x72_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x73_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21748-formula71"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x74_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>故<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x75_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p></sec><sec id="s5"><title>3. 定理的证明</title><p>定理 3.1<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的映射，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足以下条件：</p><p>1)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>2)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>3)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x84_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x85_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x86_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>4)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x87_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x88_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>对称，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x89_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x90_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x91_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>关于法向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x92_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的Steiner对称。</p><p>证明</p><p>第一步：</p><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x93_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为垂直于超平面<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x94_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的一条线段，显然<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x95_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x96_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x97_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的一点，记为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x98_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-1250554x99_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，由条件(2)